titlestmt.titleproper: Finding aid for the Alumni files

profiledesc.creation: Encoded finding aid created from MARC record by Dallas Pillen
profiledesc.langusage: The finding aid is written in English

descgrp.relatedmaterial: Files of deceased former students, 1845-ca. 1966 comprise a separate record group - Necrology Files.

archdesc.bioghist: University unit responsible for maintaining information on former University of Michigan students.
archdesc.scopecontent: Individual files on former students attending or graduating from the University of Michigan. Arranged in three records series: Alphabetical, 1845-1946 (860 boxes), Numeric, 1947-1964/65 (1000 boxes); and Entity ID, 1965-1978 (210 boxes).
